      "target": {
        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "Fix memory_search wiki fallback and plugin tool registry reuse",
        "body": "## Summary\n- add a direct memory-wiki fallback for `memory_search` and `memory_get` when wiki corpus supplements are missing at runtime\n- avoid mutating global plugin memory state during plugin tool resolution\n- add regression coverage for wiki fallback and gateway-bindable registry reuse\n\n## Problem\n`memory_search(corpus=\"wiki\")` could return no results even while `wiki_search` worked, because scoped activating plugin loads could wipe process-global memory wiki supplement registrations. Tool resolution could also over-reuse a gateway-bindable active registry that was not actually compatible with the requested plugin set.\n\n## Fix\n- add a direct `memory-wiki` fallback inside `memory-core`\n- change plugin tool resolution to reuse only compatible active registries, otherwise perform a non-activating snapshot load\n\n## Validation\n- targeted Vitest coverage for memory-core wiki fallback\n- targeted Vitest coverage for plugin tool registry reuse\n",
